source.name: NetworxBusinessVolume_FY2012_1stQtr
source.description: The dataset represents the Networx Universal and Enterprise business volume by contractor, agency, contract vehicle and month for the centralized billing account. This represents the business volume of each government agency that has ordered telecommunications services from the Networx contract.
